            "answer_text": "It helps us safely experience the emotions that are already deep inside us, that need to be experienced and expressed. If we don't experience them as emotions, they can become trapped, eventually coming out as physical pain, illness, or emotional explosions such as violence. There is also comfort in knowing that we are not alone in these emotions, that someone else wrote the music that speaks to us. ",
